title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Add more realism - changing the aircraft models used in AI mode
description:
You probably have experience it yourself when using flight simulator. You are not seeing any 3rd party aircraft model and liveries are generic and are not reflecting real airline colors. In this video we will look at the different options you can change to make the aircrafts look more realistic and also how to have a wider variety of aircrafts being shown.
